flowchart TB
  %% Diagram 76: Five-Tier Subscription Entitlement Decision Flow

  Select[Vendor selects current plan]
  Tier{Current tier}

  Free[Free entitlements]
  Starter[Starter entitlements]
  Growth[Growth entitlements]
  Pro[Pro entitlements]
  Enterprise[Enterprise entitlements]

  FeatureReq[Runtime feature request]
  Check{Feature allowed for tier?}
  Allow[Grant access]
  Prompt[Show upgrade prompt]

  Select --> Tier
  Tier -- Free --> Free --> FeatureReq
  Tier -- Starter --> Starter --> FeatureReq
  Tier -- Growth --> Growth --> FeatureReq
  Tier -- Pro --> Pro --> FeatureReq
  Tier -- Enterprise --> Enterprise --> FeatureReq

  FeatureReq --> Check
  Check -- Yes --> Allow
  Check -- No --> Prompt
